inputs.name: settingsFileName
inputs.purpose: (String) Treatment Optimization settings file

inputs.name: resultsDirectories
inputs.purpose: (String) Results directories to plot from instead of the directory specified in the given settings file

inputs.name: modelFileName
inputs.purpose: (String) .osim model used in the Treatment Optimization run

inputs.name: trackedDataFile
inputs.purpose: (String) File containing tracked joint angles for the Treatment Optimization Run

inputs.name: resultsDataFiles
inputs.purpose: (List of Strings) Files containing results joint angles from the Treatment Optimization Run

inputs.name: useRadians
inputs.purpose: (Logical) Flag specifying whether to plot in radians or degrees. Default is false

inputs.name: columnsToUse
inputs.purpose: (List of Strings) Column names to plot in the given .sto or .mot files.

inputs.name: columnNames
inputs.purpose: (List of Strings) Specify the names to use in subplot titles (ie plot 'Right Hip' instead of 'hip_flexion_r'.) Must be the same dimension as columnsToUse

inputs.name: legend
inputs.purpose: (List of Strings) Specify legend values to use instead of the default.

inputs.name: showRmse
inputs.purpose: (Logical) Flag specifying whether to display RMSE values for each subplot. Default is true

inputs.name: figureGridSize
inputs.purpose: (List of int) List with [FigureWidth, FigureHeight]
